      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, I\u2019m a bit sad to see this beauty go, but it's time for it to find a new home. This car is an absolute gem\u2014it\u2019s in pristine, mint condition and has been totally babied since day one. It looks and drives just like it rolled off the showroom floor! If you've been searching for something that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, you've found it. Drop me a message and come see it for yourself\u2014you're going to love it!",
      "price": 44500.0,
