    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This 997.2 Carrera S is a definitive example of naturally aspirated precision. The 3.8L flat-six features Direct Fuel Injection (DFI), providing a robust torque curve and surgical throttle response. The 6-speed manual transaxle remains crisp, with flawless synchros and a heavy, communicative clutch feel. Equipped with Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM), the chassis maintains optimal kinematic integrity with zero bushing deflection. The exterior retains its factory depth and luster, while the undercarriage is free of any fluid weepage or oxidation. This is a mechanically superlative specimen with a clean DME report and no over-revs, offering an uncompromising analog driving experience.",
      "price": 49500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
