    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive excellence that must be seen to be fully appreciated. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained by a single enthusiast owner and stored in a climate-controlled environment. The exterior paintwork is absolutely flawless, retaining its deep, mirror-like factory luster without a single stone chip, swirl mark, or blemish. Every body panel is perfectly aligned, and the original alloy wheels are free of any curb rash. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather upholstery remains supple and taut, still carrying that distinct new-car scent. There is zero wear on the seat bolsters, and every electronic component\u2014from the high-fidelity sound system to the navigation\u2014functions exactly as it did on day one. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach. It comes with a comprehensive, documented service history from authorized dealerships, ensuring that every fluid flush and inspection was performed on schedule. The engine bay is clean enough to eat off of, and the undercarriage shows no signs of road salt or inclement weather use. This is not just a used car; it is a collector-grade investment for the discerning buyer who demands perfection in every detail.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
